import React from 'react' import { UilTemperature, UilTear, UilWind, UilSun, UilSunset, } from "@iconscout/react-unicons"; import { formatTLT} from "../makeitwork/weather" function Temperature({ weather: { description, temp, feels_like, temp_min, temp_max, humidity, name, dt, country, sunrise, sunset, iconurl, speed, timezone, }, }) { return (

Thursday, 18 January 2024 | Local time: 15:31

{`${name}, ${country}`}

34°

{description}

{`${temp.toFixed()}°`}

Feels like: {`${feels_like.toFixed()}°`}

|

Humidity: {`${humidity.toFixed()}%`}

|

Wind: {`${speed.toFixed()} km/h`}

Rise:{" "} {formatTLT(sunrise, timezone, "hh:mm a")}

|

Set:{" "} {formatTLT(sunset, timezone, "hh:mm a")}

|

High:{" "} {`${temp_max.toFixed()}°`}

|

Low:{" "} {`${temp_min.toFixed()}°`}

) } export default Temperature
